				<div class="elementor-widget-container">
									UTL Solar is a well rounded leader in the solar energy and power backup industry, dealing in manufacturing and supplying solar panels, inverters, and batteries. The company was founded in 1996 by 2 proficient engineers Mr Yogesh Dua and Mr Pawan Garg. With 4 manufacturing units, we offer a diverse portfolio of 522 product SKUs. Our products are easily accessible through a network of 725 distributors, 5,546 dealers, and 1,100 exclusive Shoppe franchisees. Backed by 29 years of experience, we deliver sustainable solar solutions to support India&#8217;s renewable energy transition.								</div>
